name: Supertank
overview: A crosshairs tank shooter that was released as part of "Arcade Games" pack and in 1984, COMPUTE!'s Gazette/COMPUTE! Publications, Inc. as Supertank. Additionally it was part of COMPUTE!'s Third Book of Commodore 64. The game also got translations to Dutch and Italian. The Dutch version was published by Holt, Rinehart and Winston Ltd. as a type-in listing from the book "16 voor de 64" Also released in Italy in the following: Super VIC & C64 A2-N04 (April 1985), Jackson Soft Compilation #4
